Miscellaneous Orders.

No. 254, Misc. Schectman v. Foster, Warden. Petitioner pro se. Nathaniel L. Goldstein, Attorney General of New York, Wendell P. Brown, Solicitor General, Herman N. Harcourt and George A. Radz, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

The motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari is denied.
